ToDo manager for vdir (iCalendar) files.

USAGE
  tdx <command> [<args>...]

COMMANDS
  list, ls       list todos
  add, a         add todo
  done, do       complete todos
  purge          remove completed todos

ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
  TDX_PATH
        (required) path to vdir root directory
  TDX_DEFAULT_LIST
        list to use for <list> and <add> commands
        can be overridden with '-l'
  TDX_DEFAULT_STATUS
        status filter for <list> command
        values: NEEDS-ACTION (default), COMPLETED, CANCELLED, ANY
  TDX_DEFAULT_DUE
        due duration for new todos
        default value: 48h
  TDX_COLOR
        use color in output
        values: 1 (default), 0

FLAGS
  -v    print version
  -h    print help

Use "tdx <command> -h" for command usage.
